data.description: Quiet oasis of peace out in the country, but only 50 minutes to downtown Nashville, and 14 minutes to downtown Dickson. Very easy to show. Partial split level up to bonus room over garage, currently used as a music room. Floors, paint and kitchen updated in the last year. New gas stove installed, used to be electric. Park-like setting with new professional landscaping in the front. Deer pass through regularly and may be observed from the back deck, or treehouse. Borders a working farm through the woods. Friendly neighbors all around. Two-car garage currently utilized as a gym. Aggregate driveway from road to garage. Pride of ownership apparent! 14x26 back deck. 10x16 detached storage building. LVP flooring installed over finished oak floors to match rooms perfectly.
